4.1. Identiﬁcation of the novel splicing mutation using minigene assay

A signiﬁcant fraction of disease-causing mutations affect pre-mRNA
splicing. In the present study, three potential splice mutations as well
as one deﬁnite splice mutation (c.1032G NA) in the intron 7 5′ splice-site

