individuals and mutation carriers. Currents were recorded at various membrane potentials from −70 to +30 mV for 3 s in 10 mV increments from a holding potential of −80 mV. A
total of 10 ng of cRNA was injected with the relative ratios of WT and mutant KCNQ1 inferred from the data obtained in the real-time RT-PCR experiment. All the current recordings
